      <article>
        <h2>Creation of Iron Man</h2>
        <time datetime="05-2008">May, 2008</time>
        <figure>
          <figcaption>Anthony Stark, a genius, playboy, billionaire, philanthropist was kidnapped by a terrorist organization called the Ten Rings. When he discovered that they were using his weapons for terrorism, he decided to close his shop. To escape from capture, he developed a suit and later modified it with the help of his trusted AI- J.A.R.V.I.S. He found out that the CFO of his company, Obadiah Stane was behind his capture and had also gained control over his prototype armor which he had used to escape. He fought against 'Iron Monger' and defeated him. Then he revealed himself as Iron Man in front of the world.</figcaption>
        </figure>
